{
  "texts": [
    "(L.2)) to generate flux densities that smoothly varied in all directions.",
    "Comrade's raster model is similar to THEMIS in Sect. 5.1.4, except that we used the B-spline kernel.",
    "A detailed description of the image model is given in Appendix L.",
    "The hyperparameters of the model are the FOV and raster size (N x ×N y).",
    "For April 21 bands 3 and 4, we used a 12×12 pixel raster with a 7.5 µas pixel size, which was ∼1/3 of the nominal resolution and FOV of 90 µas."
  ]
}